pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: portfolio.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Karol M. Orozco
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  citations-hover: true
  footnotes-hover: true
  theme:
    light: ../LightTheme.css
    dark: DarkTheme.scss
  code-copy: true
  title-block-banner: true
  title: Portfolio
  listing:
    - id: projects
      contents: '{Business,Data_viz_others}/*/*.qmd'
      sort: date desc
  type: default
  date-format: long
  fields:
    - image
    - date
    - title
    - author
    - description
    - categories
    - reading-time
  sort-ui: false
  filter-ui: false
  page-layout: article

Watching files for changes
Browse at http://localhost:3420/projects/portfolio.html
